{"tid":532789,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印花婆婆若屬萬寧僱員 遭即時解僱或失代通知金","createTime":"2018-01-18T07:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T07:48:37.000Z","uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f1f0ddc922aff848213d41667b16ebd2a5991262","tid":532789,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T07:35:46.000Z","msg":"2018-01-18 13:43:34 HKT\t<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180118/large/1516256073_46be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180118%2Flarge%2F1516256073_46be.jpg&h=dd8bb9f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據庭上資料，印花婆婆前後在三間萬寧工作10多年，暫時未確定她是否萬寧正式僱員。如果是正式僱員，職工盟統籌幹事王宇來分析，若僱主以員工犯嚴重過失為由作即時解僱，便無須賠償長期服務金和代通知金。他指僱主在解僱時，無須強而有力的證據，員工的角色被動和欠缺保障，若法庭月底裁定婆婆無罪，婆婆仍須循民事追討解僱賠償，一旦雙方未達成共識，便需要由勞資審裁處審理。<br />\n<br />\n根據現時條例，僱主在以下情況，可即時解僱僱員，而無須預先通知或給予代通知金，包括僱員在與其僱傭有關的事宜上，故意不服從僱主合法合理的命令、行為不當、欺詐、不忠實或慣常疏忽職責。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180118/57722788\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180118%2F57722788&d=K57mQQZxUvxwTeepu0IeDO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=ae53b427\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180118%2F57722788&h=05c0900e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180118/57722788</a>"},{"pid":"6dfe391b9ea8eaf30a3e29a4f94a15738948c3a3","tid":532789,"uid":65186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T07:45:19.000Z","msg":"啲人成日話淨係個保安錯,萬寧唔知道咁,根本係冇可能,人地計過條數有著數先做"},{"pid":"ca38fbf54e1b1495c2299fe2989634cf34ecd9b1","tid":532789,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T07:46:56.000Z","msg":"有冇可能性？<br />\nd記者點寫架 咁唔通順都出得街"},{"pid":"1ee34738c318cc3a14c1cdfa57c7b9eacc91d698","tid":532789,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6dfe391b9ea8eaf30a3e29a4f94a15738948c3a3","tid":532789,"uid":65186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T07:45:19.000Z","msg":"啲人成日話淨係個保安錯,萬寧唔知道咁,根本係冇可能,人地計過條數有著數先做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T07:47:38.000Z","msg":"我相信保安話要報警萬寧一定話ok先得<br />\n咁既然要報，萬寧個分店經理係咪有責任check清楚自己既CCTV片先叫差佬黎呢？"},{"pid":"bfa9320cb239da1b782add4451a1e0c5be39f580","tid":532789,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T07:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好賠囉 我呢世唔黎買野"},{"pid":"9c5fb399d8e679760f0948d146b563b189feb2b3","tid":532789,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T07:48:37.000Z","msg":"外判啦"}]}